node.text: Last week, we launched our exclusive On Point Collection at the VS Studio in sunny Los Angeles. node.text: It’s an all-out Panty Party! For a limited-time only, shop 7/$35.

We got you, Mama. Designed to support you while nursing, the much-anticipated Body by Victoria Maternity Bra blends functional details with supreme comfort so that underneath it all, you feel like yourself.

Destination: staycation. Whether exploring a new restaurant in your own city, finally reading a new book, or enjoying an afternoon snooze, our at-home picks transport you straight to a vacation state of mind.
Final boarding call for summer’s last hurrah! We’ve confirmed your beachside essentials with Swim separates, velour sets, and fresh fragrances that guarantee you’re ready for the long-weekend.
